metadata.description: Big Bugs is a collection of 10,000 NFTs on the Ethereum Blockchain â€” each Big Bug comes with its own unique combination of over 150 hand drawn assets, meaning no two Bugs are the same. Designed by a female artist, this is a community based project that aims to give back to not only our holders, but also to charities and not for profit organisations that align with our values.
